  "id": "019d442a-0a15-7ca3-b9db-55272df7c7b3",
  "content": "ckground: linear-gradient(160deg, #0f172a 0%, #1a2332 50%, #0f172a 100%);\">\n  <div class=\"slide-label\">Key Takeaways</div>\n  <div class=\"slide-title\" style=\"margin-bottom: 40px;\">\n    What I've<br>\n    <span class=\"highlight\">Learned So Far</span>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 28px; margin-bottom: 40px;\">\n    <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 20px;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 32px; flex-shrink: 0;\">&#128161;</div>\n      <div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700;\">Instrument at design time, not after the fire</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 22px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 8px; line-height: 1.5;\">Span contracts defined before the code existed. Every new feature gets traces automatically.</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 20px;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 32px; flex-shrink: 0;\">&#128065;</div>\n      <div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700;\">Observability without control is a dashboard with no buttons</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 22px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 8px; line-height: 1.5;\">The agent needs graduated permission to act on what it sees. Not just watch.</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 20px;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 32px; flex-shrink: 0;\">&#128274;</div>\n      <div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700;\">Safety tiers are the agent equivalent of \"are you sure?\"</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 22px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 8px; line-height: 1.5;\">Built on MCP's existing primitives. Read freely. Mutate with preview. Destructive ops need dry-run.</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 20px;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 32px; flex-shrink: 0;\">&#127793;</div>\n      <div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700;\">I'm still early. The tools are shipped. The workflows are forming.</div>",
